name: The Chedi Muscat
about_short: Among the hotels and resorts in Oman, The Chedi Muscat offers one of the best experiences of Arabic hospitality in a lavish beach resort. Get inspired here!
about_long: Among the hotels and resorts in Oman, The Chedi Muscat offers one of the best experiences of Arabic hospitality in a lavish beach resort. Get inspired here! Where the majestic Al Hajar Mountains meet their luminous reflection in the serene waters of the Gulf of Oman, The Chedi Muscat rises amidst an elegantly landscaped twenty-one-acre garden oasis with 162 Omani-influenced guestrooms and villas. The 5-star luxury beach resort in Muscat is Oman’s first contemporary beach hotel which opened its doors in 2003.
